ZH: 请站稳栏杆上。
EN: Please stand steady on the railing.

ZH: 不要动，站稳不要掉下来。
EN: Don't move, stand still and don't fall off.

ZH: 站稳不要晃动，车正在颠簸。
EN: Stand firm and don't sway, the car is bumping.

ZH: 孩子，站稳了才能踢球。
EN: Child, you need to stand steady before you can kick the ball.

ZH: 大家一起来，站稳队列。
EN: Everyone, come together and stand steady in line.

ZH: 请排队，站稳不要挤。
EN: Please queue up, stand steady and don't push.

ZH: 老人请站稳，我给您让座。
EN: Elderly person, please stand steady, I'll give up my seat for you.

ZH: 乘客们，请站稳，火车即将发车。
EN: Passengers, please stand steady, the train is about to depart.

ZH: 队员们，站稳动作准备开始。
EN: Team members, stand steady and get ready for action.

ZH: 不要失去平衡，要站稳。
EN: Don't lose your balance, stay steady.

ZH: 演讲要坚定、自信、站稳。
EN: Speeches require determination, confidence, and standing steady.

ZH: 驾驶员请抓紧方向盘，站稳脚踏板。
EN: Drivers, please hold the steering wheel firmly and stand steady on the pedals.

ZH: 站稳了再慢慢往前走。
EN: Stand steady and then walk slowly forward.

ZH: 请保持站稳，不要晃动。
EN: Please maintain a steady stance and don't sway.

ZH: 我感觉站得不稳，手心都出汗了。
EN: I feel unsteady standing, my palms are sweating.

ZH: 没有站稳的根基，无法迈向成功。
EN: Without a firm foundation, it is impossible to move towards success.

ZH: 目的坚定，站稳脚跟。
EN: Stay determined and stand firm on your ground.

ZH: 当我们身处风雨中，我们必须站稳。
EN: When we are in the storm, we must stand steady.

ZH: 不要因困难而退缩，我们必须站稳。
EN: Don't retreat because of difficulties, we must stand firm.

ZH: 勇敢站稳，面对挑战。
EN: Stand bravely and face the challenges.
